{
  "text": "In the present study all cultures were started from normal thoracic aortic rings, prepared from adult rats. It has already been concluded by others [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ) that phenotypic alteration from contractile to synthetic -like in the formation of atherosclerotic and restenotic lesions -also occurs when SMC are grown in culture.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "42495684",
    "[CITATION_2]": "40842065"
  },
